data.description: DUPLEX/Multi-Family investment, OWNER-OCCUPIED/RENTAL OR Large Single Family. Move-in-ready ranch-style living with this impressive property featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths on the main level, plus a fully finished walkout lower level with 1 bedroom and 1 full bath. Enjoy the flexibility and versatility of two full kitchens, two laundry rooms, two family rooms, and two separate driveways, all complemented by a completely separate entrance. Impeccably maintained with tasteful colors throughout.  Don't miss out on this chance to call this beautiful property your own. Schedule a private showing today!
